Flow syntax support.</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"data-store\"><a href=\"#data-store\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Data Store</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/reduxjs/react-redux\">Redux</a> ide o glob√°lny obchod s premenn√Ωmi. Je vhodn√Ω k tomu,\naby ste nemuseli preposiela≈• premenn√∫ cez ƒèal≈°√≠ch <em>x</em> komponent do hƒ∫bky. Tak ju\nnapoj√≠te na glob√°lne obchod. Pou≈æitie napr√≠klad: user data, aktu√°lna t√©ma, stav aplik√°cie, ‚Ä¶\nPou≈æ√≠va sa ƒçasto. Odpor√∫ƒçam si doin≈°talova≈• na v√Ωvijanie <a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/redux-devtools/lmhkpmbekcpmknklioeibfkpmmfibljd?hl=en\">plugin</a> do chrome.\nAk sa chcete vyhn√∫≈• boilerplate, ktor√Ω je spojen√Ω s Reduxom, odpor√∫ƒçam <a href=\"https://github.com/rematch/rematch\">rematch</a>.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/5f59d/redux.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 38.24091778202677%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Redux\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/fb8a0/redux.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/1a291/redux.png 148w,\n/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/2bc4a/redux.png 295w,\n/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/fb8a0/redux.png 590w,\n/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/526de/redux.png 885w,\n/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/fa2eb/redux.png 1180w,\n/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/5f59d/redux.png 1569w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://reactjs.org/docs/context.html\">React Context</a> je to pomerne nov√° feature od Reactu.\nJe teoretick√Ωm nahraditeƒæom Reduxu. Tu sa, ale vytvor√≠ <code class=\"language-text\">provider</code> d√°t a\njeho vn√∫torn√© komponenty vo vn√∫tri ich vedia ƒçita≈• pomocou <code class=\"language-text\">consumera</code>.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a79300f87d3c6b1b8355615b213cdb07/fe66f/react-context.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 321px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 70.40498442367601%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"React Context\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/a79300f87d3c